Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.89,0:02:23.25,OPJP P,,0,0,0,,時{\fsp5}に{\fnFOT-Carat Std UB\fs80\fsp5}曖昧{\fn\fs}で見失う
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:25.91,OPJP P,,0,0,0,,戸惑いがちな自分でも
