Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好幸福呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.87,0:03:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,听说亚子和Roselia的大家去了海边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,她们在海边的音乐工作室里强化合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.65,0:03:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Afterglow的成员在图书馆里写了暑假作业
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.91,0:04:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那里好凉爽 能呆上一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,听说Hello,Happy World也去了很凉快的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,反而Pastel*Palettes好像去了更热的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.35,0:04:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 RAISE A SUILEN…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那是来参观了Popipa主办演唱会的乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,现在好像很受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把你们全毁了 给我做好觉悟啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然那之后我就没关注了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那个“全毁了”到底是什么意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.16,0:04:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,毁了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,毁（压扁）？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,压扁压扁 揉一揉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.29,0:04:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,压扁压扁 揉一揉呀揉一揉！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,揉一揉！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要弄成团子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.29,0:05:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是团子耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人一串哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真对不起 她们那么吵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 毕竟外面那么冷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.86,0:05:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我在的时候欢迎随时过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真的幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.77,0:05:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好糯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,给 沙绫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.78,0:05:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有咲 心情真好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了 你是在期待今天的仓库练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,猜中了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,才没猜中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但是有咲你起得那么早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,大家好久没在仓库里一起见面了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,倒也不至于那么久啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,今天放学之后也没学生会的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,没有打工
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们家今天也没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,里美今天也不用补课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 一开始就能过去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样 怎么样 要做什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,都说要练习了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,有哪的窗户没关吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,把小火炉拿去有咲家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.18,0:06:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,小火炉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,放在哪儿了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,在教室
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.43,0:06:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 你要跟到哪去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,E班在那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,也对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,多惠！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好暖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这帮人又开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟冷嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.99,0:06:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,里美 有咲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这边取暖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Popipa还真精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy！Lucky！Smile…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,心！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello Happy还真精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.43,0:07:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,请路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才那位我觉得还挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,哪好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,RAISE A SUILEN可是最强的乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.59,0:07:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,半桶水的吉他手可是No thank you的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但是难道要一直靠外援的吉他手开演唱会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不是一直
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.41,0:07:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 如果不是只为我奏响的吉他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,就不能把Roselia毁了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前就想问你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,“毁了”是要干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你没在想什么危险的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,当然！我是要让他们心服口服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,具体要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经找好了最适合的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,总之 在找到最棒的吉他手之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.58,0:07:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,面试要一直继续
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.27,0:07:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你们就专心训练
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:07:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:07:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,PAREO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:07:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,在 CHU²大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,要肉干是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No！给我把下一个面试选手叫来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,快去！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才那位就是最后一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,仓练 仓练
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.83,0:08:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,话说你面包买太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.61,0:08:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我肚子饿了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得只买一只太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,“只”？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说米歇尔面包吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这是秋季的新品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道LOCK在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,去分她一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微等等哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,等会要尝尝米歇尔面包吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.25,0:08:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.73,0:08:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,香澄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.29,0:08:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,有坏人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.94,0:08:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,BanG Dream！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,武道馆！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,说是武道馆哦 武道馆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.48,0:08:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 武道馆！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 这下热闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:09:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这下真热闹了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,麻里奈 这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.55,0:09:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这是附近的Live House一起策划的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们努力拿下武道馆了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.99,0:09:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真厉害啊 兰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.75,0:09:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 虽然必须得拼进决赛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,一起去吧 武道馆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 干嘛没人配合我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.60,0:09:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,友希那 友希那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你不出场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.62,0:09:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们要准备Future World Fes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,现在分不了这个心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,亚子 你对武道馆有兴趣的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,亚子 那是摇滚的圣地哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.95,0:09:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那出场吧 一起参加啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Galaxy也是预选赛场地之一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我是刚刚听说的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,武道馆 好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,太厉害啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好像要根据观众的投票赢得高排位才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,大概有多少乐队要参加呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,参加吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.53,0:10:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,有咲你之前也说过想去武道馆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,追寻同一个梦想 真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得哪天能上武道馆也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那才不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,“这个”？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 大家有共同的梦想真好…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不对！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不是…也没有啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.67,0:10:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不知道能不能进入决赛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.10,0:11:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一起努力也挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,有咲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,有咲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,有咲也来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Popipa Pipopa
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.83,0:11:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Popipapa Pipopa！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.89,0:11:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,目标武道馆！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.05,0:11:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,LOCK也要参加吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.51,0:11:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,LOCK也加入Popipa 一起登上武道馆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这行不通的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,要我加入Popipa什么的 不敢当啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你对武道馆没兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,倒不是没有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不行的不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.71,0:11:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我很感激
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,太烦人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.28,0:11:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 让你们费心了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就是因为我没有乐队吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:11:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.59,0:12:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,明明你从春天开始就一直在募集成员
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,照这样下去还能不能找到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,LOCK的吉他明明弹得那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,文化祭那次真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,要不还是要加入Popipa吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你找到乐队成员
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,再见咯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Popipa的各位真温柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我最喜欢Popipa了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 贵安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,说错了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.61,0:13:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,请问 你是益木吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.19,0:13:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 我是第一次看你穿校服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.41,0:13:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你是高中生的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我不是这个意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.98,0:13:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在吵什么架呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.54,0:13:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,才没吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 益木 你这样坐着裙子要皱的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,她不是在这附近的学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是从幼儿园到大学一应俱全 名叫白雪学院的名媛学校哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然是名媛 但她又整天泡在父亲开的Live House里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是真正的深闺大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1147,970)}箱入り娘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,深闺…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 是指Live House的包厢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:13:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我去打一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,在乐队还挺顺利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是叫RAISE A SUILEN吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,名字太长了 叫RAS就行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 是那个“揉团子”的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet！Excellent！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你最喜欢Roselia了对吧 CHU²
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,才不！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你一直在看Roselia的视频哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我这是在研究对手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,确实她们是精彩出色的乐队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是越强越有打败的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要用自己的音乐问鼎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要什么制作人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,凑友希那 竟然敢小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,俗话说爱之深责之切…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.45,0:15:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No PAREO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.95,0:15:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你妨碍着我了 快走开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会妨碍你了 请让我呆在这
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,肉干
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes PAREO！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,文化祭… 新的视频
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.35,0:15:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,大家请尝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.77,0:15:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,武道馆演唱会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你太着急啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.57,0:15:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,表象训练很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:16:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 我完全想象不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟武道馆就像做梦一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 Bang！Dream！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.89,0:16:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,呃… 我还想再见姐姐一面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,里美 沙绫！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,逮捕！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,BanG Dream 是这意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉打扰各位休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.93,0:16:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢各位的声援
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,私闯民宅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.53,0:16:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是从正门进来 让您奶奶带路到这的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.75,0:16:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,十分抱歉没有事先预约
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.75,0:16:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1210,970)}Appointment
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Appoi？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.55,0:16:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这是会面的客套话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,PAREO…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这回是什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要那么警戒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是来给您把这个带过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.97,0:16:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那么再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.47,0:17:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,并… 不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,您能记住我 不胜荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,再次自我介绍 我是CHU²的键盘手女仆 PAREO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,您好 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.01,0:17:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,朝日六花小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,7月17日出生 巨蟹座 A血型
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,岐阜县出身 从春天开始住在这家澡堂里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,早晨要打扫浴室 白天上学 晚上…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,请问 你怎么知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我查到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.23,0:17:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这是您的请帖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,请帖？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.82,0:17:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会把你带上一个全新的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Poppin'party也会到场的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Popipa吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.37,0:17:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.99,0:18:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,RAS的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,单独演唱会？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,观众好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,之前都够多了 这次还更多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,沙绫她们马上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.87,0:18:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.49,0:18:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 你们来了啊 就两个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.07,0:18:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不 五个人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,难道Popipa收到请帖了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 Roselia也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.05,0:18:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟对方来请了好多次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.37,0:18:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,她们自称女子乐队大时代的新领袖 这点我也很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:19:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,女子乐队大时代的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.31,0:19:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,新领袖？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.17,0:19:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,多惠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,里美和沙绫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.02,0:19:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,在看物贩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,LOCK 你怎么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.48,0:19:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我差点被人流淹没 多惠学姐救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,一杆钓起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.67,0:19:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我不愿意来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.23,0:19:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但难得对方邀请了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.18,0:19:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,LOCK也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.48,0:19:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子 在想什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,RAS RAS RAS…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.61,0:20:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗 超乎我想象了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,吉他是事先录的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 但就算这样 演奏还是很出色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,果然好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,多惠学姐 你曾经在那上面演奏的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,KING Yeah！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.25,0:21:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.71,0:21:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,在唱安可曲之前先来一个精彩的告知哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我的乐队 RAISE A SUILEN
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,将要参加BanG Dream！女子乐队挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那么那么 重要的还在后头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.44,0:21:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我要在BanG Dream里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,把Roselia和Popipa给亲手毁掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.49,0:21:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,团子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,为了实现这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.01,0:21:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,六花·朝日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我要将你收入麾下
